import styled from 'styled-components/native';

export const MenuContainer = styled.View`
    align-items: center,
    justify-content: center,
    flex-direction: row,
    margi-top: .5rem,
    margin-bottom: 1rem,
    backgroundColor: gray,
    borderRadius: 1rem,
    width: 80%,
`;

export const Pointer = styled.Text`
    color: text_primary,
    font-size: 1.5rem,
    margin-left: .5rem,
    marginRight: .5rem,
    font-weight: bold,
`;
